Global Bedsore Air Cushion Market Insights
Bedsore Air Cushion Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Bedsore Air Cushion Market Overview
The global bedsore air cushion market is poised for significant growth, with the market size projected to reach USD 1.35 billion by 2027, expanding at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2020 to 2027. This growth is driven by the increasing prevalence of chronic diseases, rising geriatric population, and the growing awareness regarding the prevention of pressure ulcers in healthcare settings. Additionally, advancements in technology have led to the development of more effective air cushion products, further contributing to the market's expansion. North America and Europe are expected to dominate the market due to the higher adoption rate of advanced healthcare technologies and growing demand for bedsore prevention products.

